<div class="hero-unit">
  <h1>Bloccit</h1>
  <p>Bloccit is a resource for sharing links with your friends!</p>
  <p>
      <%= link_to "Login", new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-large' %> or 
      <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-success btn-large' %> today!
  </p>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Bloccit = Reddit</h2>
    <p>Reddit is a famous internet blog. Bloccit is a copy of the way that blog works and looks. If you don't know about Reddit you should leave this site now!</p>
  </div>
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Tutorial on Rails</h2>
    <p>The Bloccit tutorial is a great way to quickly get up to speed with basic Rails concepts like MVC structure, Gems, Mailers, view templates, basic model & controller methods, and more.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Created by Bloc</h2>
    <p>If you're serious about wanting to learn how to code, you should check out <%= link_to "Bloc", "http://bloc.io/" %>.</p>
  </div>
</div>